{%- comment -%}
  Renders per-service FAQ questions for a given product handle.
  Usage: {%- render 'service-faq', product: product -%}
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign h = product.handle -%}

{%- if h == 'auction-tenanted-property-pre-sale-legal-pack' or h == 'auction-legal-pack' -%}

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>What is an Auction Legal Pack?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>An Auction Legal Pack is a set of legal documents prepared by a solicitor that potential buyers review before bidding. It includes title documents, property searches, Special Conditions of Sale, and any relevant certificates — everything needed for due diligence.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>How long does it take to prepare?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>A complete Auction Legal Pack is typically prepared within 5–7 working days. We'll keep you updated throughout the process and confirm when it's ready for your auctioneer.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>Do I need a legal pack for every auction?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Yes — virtually all UK auction houses require a legal pack to be available before the property is listed. Without one, bidders cannot carry out due diligence, which typically results in fewer bids and a lower sale price.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>Can I use this for tenanted property sales?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Absolutely. Our legal pack covers both vacant and tenanted properties. For tenanted sales, we include copies of existing tenancy agreements, rent schedules, and any relevant notices alongside the standard pack.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

{%- elsif h == 'survey-photography-service' or h == 'rics-level-2-survey' -%}

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>What does a RICS Level 2 Survey cover?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>A RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Survey assesses the overall condition of the property, highlighting any significant defects, potential risks, and areas that may require further investigation. It uses a traffic-light system to rate each element.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>Are your surveyors RICS regulated?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Yes. All surveys are carried out by fully qualified, RICS-regulated surveyors. The Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors sets the professional standards for the property industry, so every report is thorough, impartial, and compliant.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>How quickly will I receive the report and photos?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>The survey report is typically delivered within 3–5 working days of the visit. Edited photographs are usually ready within 48 hours. Both are sent to you digitally.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>Is the listing boost included automatically?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Yes — the listing boost is bundled into this service. Once your photos are ready, we activate premium placement across Rightmove, Zoopla, and OnTheMarket at no additional cost.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

{%- elsif h == 'outlays' -%}

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>What exactly are outlays?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Outlays are third-party fees incurred during a property transaction — such as Local Authority searches, Land Registry charges, and Drainage & Water searches. Rather than tracking and paying these individually, we handle everything on your behalf.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>Are there any hidden fees on top?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>No. The price you pay covers all standard outlay costs. You'll receive a full itemised breakdown showing exactly what was paid and to whom — complete transparency.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="product-faq__item">
    <summary class="product-faq__question">
      <span>What searches are included?</span>
      <svg class="product-faq__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="product-faq__answer">
      <p>Standard searches include Local Authority, Drainage & Water, Environmental, and Land Registry searches. If your transaction requires additional searches, we'll discuss this with you before proceeding.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

